19:25.465 --> 19:26.534
I wish it was that easy.

19:26.567 --> 19:29.971
- I need to walk. Right now.
- Okay.

19:30.004 --> 19:34.207
Lea, if you violate your
promise after they let you out,

19:34.241 --> 19:35.543
you'll be begging for
the four to nine years,

19:35.576 --> 19:36.544
they're currently offering you.

19:36.577 --> 19:37.812
Four to nine.

19:37.845 --> 19:39.113
I might've plead you
down at two

19:39.147 --> 19:40.648
if you kept your mouth
shut about cooperating.

19:40.682 --> 19:43.183
Right, let the system do its
magic.

19:44.484 --> 19:45.485
You know how hard it is to live

19:45.520 --> 19:47.187
with a rap sheet hanging over
you?

19:48.990 --> 19:50.124
How hard I had to hustle

19:50.158 --> 19:52.060
to even get a shit job at the
tow pound?

19:54.428 --> 19:56.329
I have to get out, I have to get
out.

19:56.363 --> 19:57.397
All right, all right.

19:57.431 --> 19:58.900
So plead not guilty, and drop
bail.

19:58.933 --> 20:00.367
Look, if you're right about
this questionable stop,

20:00.400 --> 20:01.836
we have a shot at getting
this thing dismissed.

20:01.869 --> 20:03.270
- I promise you.
- Bail.

20:04.438 --> 20:05.740
Jesus, if I had 50,000,

20:05.773 --> 20:06.841
you'd think I'd be

20:06.874 --> 20:08.042
- in this mess?
- Whoa, whoa, 50,000?

20:08.076 --> 20:09.877
What judge set that number?

20:09.911 --> 20:12.345
- Some fat guy.
- That narrows it down.

20:15.950 --> 20:18.186
Okay, these baddies you're
rolling.

20:19.854 --> 20:21.321
Tell me everything.

20:21.354 --> 20:22.657
No lies, please.

20:26.728 --> 20:27.562
Early bird.

20:31.099 --> 20:32.100
Spread the wealth.

20:34.869 --> 20:38.072
So this guy, Craig,
approached me a few days ago,

20:38.106 --> 20:40.307
asking questions about
a car that was towed.

20:41.909 --> 20:42.944
Before he came in,

20:42.977 --> 20:44.579
he Googled everyone at the tow
pound,

20:44.612 --> 20:46.047
guess whose mugshot came up.

20:47.548 --> 20:49.851
Knowing I had a record,
he offered me 100 grand

20:49.884 --> 20:50.885
if I'd help him out.

20:52.053 --> 20:53.855
Help him, how?

20:53.888 --> 20:55.056
By grabbing a sample of the
heroin

20:55.089 --> 20:57.091
that was stashed inside that
Navigator.

21:09.937 --> 21:12.106
I thought it'd be easy money.

21:12.140 --> 21:14.742
Instead I was arrested
coming back from the preview.

21:16.677 --> 21:18.212
Preview for what?

21:18.246 --> 21:20.615
Craig needed the
sample to set up a deal.

21:20.648 --> 21:22.750
He plans to buy the car
at the tow pounds auction,

21:22.784 --> 21:24.652
before anyone else finds out
about it.

21:26.788 --> 21:28.288
So who did the drugs
belong to?

21:28.321 --> 21:29.624
A Mexican cartel.

21:30.457 --> 21:31.458
Jesus, Lea.

21:33.261 --> 21:34.494
Their mule lost the
cargo

21:34.529 --> 21:36.864
while he was visiting
his girlfriend in Queens.

21:38.699 --> 21:41.235
And the girlfriend
told Craig about it?

21:41.269 --> 21:44.038
Yeah, she was hooking
up with Craig on the side.

21:46.373 --> 21:47.407
Why?

21:47.440 --> 21:50.310
Why risk it?

21:50.343 --> 21:52.513
I was tired of my life.

21:52.547 --> 21:53.514
You're late.

21:53.548 --> 21:54.682
Just getting my game face on.

21:54.715 --> 21:56.083
There are other ways to the
game

21:56.117 --> 21:58.519
if you wanna trade that window
for a desk.

21:58.553 --> 22:00.855
And I saw an
opportunity to change it.

22:03.224 --> 22:04.859
So, I jumped.

22:21.909 --> 22:22.810
You warned me.

22:24.512 --> 22:25.345
About?

22:27.648 --> 22:29.550
The people I let into my life.

22:30.585 --> 22:31.953
I'm always letting myself be
chosen,

22:31.986 --> 22:32.920
I need to choose.

22:36.924 --> 22:39.126
Here come the detectives.

22:39.160 --> 22:40.828
Be careful of what you say,
okay?

22:52.039 --> 22:55.176
Okay, your story checks out.
Dates.

22:55.209 --> 22:57.712
When is the Navigator
set to be auctioned off?

22:57.745 --> 22:58.713
A week from Wednesday.

22:58.746 --> 23:00.480
You sure about that?

23:00.514 --> 23:03.217
Wednesday is the day it all
goes down.

23:03.251 --> 23:04.417
Win the car, win the dope.

23:05.385 --> 23:07.188
- What's the play?
- Play?

23:07.221 --> 23:09.357
There's a ton of
fucking dope in that car.

23:09.389 --> 23:11.092
