convo.

24:29.537 --> 24:30.371
Check it out.

24:31.439 --> 24:32.273
Freaky, right?

24:33.541 --> 24:35.209
I can't believe I swiped
right.

24:40.047 --> 24:42.850
Anyway, you still haven't told
me

24:42.883 --> 24:44.218
