24:45.619 --> 24:46.954
I slept over at a friend's.

24:46.988 --> 24:47.788
Friends, huh?

24:47.822 --> 24:49.557
Mm-hmm, yeah.

24:50.658 --> 24:51.659
Who is he?

24:52.793 --> 24:53.627
She.

24:54.729 --> 24:56.197
And who I fuck is my business.

24:56.230 --> 24:57.064
Nice.

25:02.536 --> 25:04.872
Come on, hop in.

25:06.407 --> 25:07.541
We got somewhere to be.

25:10.211 --> 25:12.713
