in there with that?

25:12.747 --> 25:14.281
You're nuttier than I thought.

25:14.315 --> 25:15.349
Let's go.

25:15.383 --> 25:16.217
I ain't asking.

25:17.218 --> 25:18.519
You let her walk?

25:18.552 --> 25:19.887
I detect a note of skepticism.

25:19.920 --> 25:21.789
I worked in corporate America.

25:21.822 --> 25:23.157
