after like three days.

25:26.527 --> 25:27.862
A month, don't knock it.

25:32.233 --> 25:33.167
Whatever.

25:36.670 --> 25:37.972
Now, come on,

25:38.005 --> 25:40.207
how many felonies are you
handling?

25:40.241 --> 25:41.042
Right now?

25:41.075 --> 25:43.210
Oh, 80 something.

25:43.244 --> 25:46.247
All right, and how many
actually go to trial?

25:46.280 --> 25:47.882
I don't know, none.

25:50.351 --> 25:51.520
Booya motherfucker!

25:51.552 --> 25:52.887
Exactly, exactly.

25:52.920 --> 25:53.754
50 grand.

25:54.889 --> 25:56.323
