him to be stable enough

26:35.830 --> 26:37.566
to appear for sentencing.

26:37.598 --> 26:40.734
During which, he left at great
delay

26:40.768 --> 26:42.803
and aggravation to the court.

26:42.837 --> 26:45.372
Per the statutory sentencing
requirements,

26:45.406 --> 26:47.741
the court will recommend
three to six years,

26:47.775 --> 26:49.910
pending the approval of the
Department of Probation.

26:49.944 --> 26:50.911
Your Honor, you have the power

26:50.945 --> 26:52.480
to waive a mandatory minimum

26:52.514 --> 26:53.747
- if you could just authorize-
- One more word

26:53.781 --> 26:55.816
while I am speaking.

26:57.351 --> 26:58.719
Are you aware of

26:58.752 --> 27:01.722
what Mr. Coates told the
court before your arrival?

27:01.755 --> 27:03.090
No, Your Honor.

27:03.124 --> 27:04.825
Mr. Coates claimed that you
told him

27:04.859 --> 27:07.294
to leave the courtroom on his
last visit.

27:08.829 --> 27:09.830
No, I did not.

27:09.864 --> 27:11.465
You suggested he jumped off to
Cuba.

27:11.499 --> 27:12.733
That was a joke.

27:12.766 --> 27:16.170
Ah, hence the jocularity
which has ensued.

27:16.203 --> 27:17.671
He'd just been told he's
rewarded

27:17.705 --> 27:19.173
for staying clean, for not
dying,

27:19.206 --> 27:20.641
