27:20.674 --> 27:24.812
But he inferred that you
meant for him to jump bail.

27:24.845 --> 27:27.915
I'm sorry, is that what
you believe, like personally?

27:27.948 --> 27:31.118
I'm sorry, Casi, she was
yelling at me.

27:31.152 --> 27:33.154
Got me all jammed up,
and I said, whatever,

27:33.187 --> 27:34.021
you mad?

27:35.789 --> 27:38.759
How could I be mad at
someone who plays like you?

27:38.792 --> 27:41.028
Ask me how many days I last
used?

27:42.997 --> 27:43.831
How many?

27:46.133 --> 27:46.967
105.

27:50.572 --> 27:51.640
One going in.

27:57.978 --> 28:00.447
Well, now that that's out of
the way,

28:00.481 --> 28:03.817
the only thing left to consider
is your conduct, Counselor.

28:03.851 --> 28:05.352
Am I being cited?

28:05.386 --> 28:07.721
