career-ending

28:07.755 --> 28:09.490
for such a young attorney.

28:09.524 --> 28:11.292
With all due respect,

28:11.325 --> 28:13.994
- I've done this-
- Oh, why start now?

28:14.028 --> 28:16.163
You haven't done yourself
any favors before me.

28:17.364 --> 28:18.567
There are no complaints I'm
aware of.

28:18.600 --> 28:20.000
No?

28:20.034 --> 28:23.003
Then I would read the formal
complaint very closely,

28:23.037 --> 28:24.673
when it's submitted to your
superiors.

28:26.941 --> 28:28.643
Next docket.

28:59.773 --> 29:01.442
Come on, chop chop.

29:01.475 --> 29:04.111
Not until you tell me what's
going on.

29:04.144 --> 29:05.412
The Golem got in touch.

29:06.914 --> 29:08.415
I thought we were good to go.

29:08.449 --> 29:10.417
There's been a wrinkle.

29:10.451 --> 29:11.720
He says, I gotta show
up with who was with me

29:11.752 --> 29:12.654
at the preview.

29:13.787 --> 29:14.589
Aka you.

29:15.990 --> 29:16.957
- Come on.
- No.

29:20.427 --> 29:21.962
What is this place?

29:21.996 --> 29:24.298
We have a partner, remember?

29:24.331 --> 29:25.933
The reason we know what we know.

29:27.569 --> 29:28.435
The mule's girl?

29:29.970 --> 29:31.272
I know.

29:31.305 --> 29:33.508
It's time you two had
a little face to face.

29:35.909 --> 29:37.278
You, stay put.

29:39.813 --> 29:40.649
Not with him.

29:42.082 --> 29:43.817
Just you and me, that's it.

30:29.897 --> 30:30.765
Hey.

30:35.503 --> 30:36.904
Shut the fuck up!

30:38.305 --> 30:39.139
Shut up.

30:41.241 --> 30:42.677
The guys behind this shit,

30:42.711 --> 30:44.311
they must have paid her a visit.

30:45.179 --> 30:47.649
She was dead when I found her.

30:47.682 --> 30:49.383
I didn't want the cops
asking any questions

30:49.416 --> 30:50.819
that might derail this
motherfucker,

30:50.851 --> 30:52.554
so I stashed her here.

30:52.587 --> 30:53.387
You hear me?

30:55.022 --> 30:58.092
They know my name, and you.

31:02.162 --> 31:02.996
Okay?

31:06.400 --> 31:08.168
I take this away, you won't
scream?

31:09.504 --> 31:10.772
Get the fuck off me.

31:12.873 --> 31:13.874
I'm just trying to bring you

31:13.907 --> 31:15.275
into the cone of shit going down
here.

31:17.579 --> 31:19.113
So we all know the stakes.

31:31.693 --> 31:35.095
- One million.
- One million what?

31:35.129 --> 31:38.065
- That's my new cut.
- Blow me.

31:38.098 --> 31:40.134
I did, very underwhelming.

31:42.035 --> 31:44.405
You need me at a drop I
wanted nothing to do with.

31:44.438 --> 31:46.073
The crew we're ripping
off, leaving bodies behind,

31:46.106 --> 31:48.041
so I need one fucking million.

31:48.075 --> 31:50.244
That's the cost to get your 14.

31:50.277 --> 31:52.179
Plus a promise I don't
have to see your face again

31:52.212 --> 31:54.248
until the day of the auction.

31:54.281 --> 31:55.449
250, final offer.

31:57.084 --> 31:58.018
It's not gonna cut it, Craig.

31:58.051 --> 31:58.887
Come on.

31:58.919 --> 32:00.622
I'm not ending up like her.

32:00.655 --> 32:03.257
One million is a figure it takes
to get me out of this life,

32:03.290 --> 32:04.124
on my terms.

32:12.567 --> 32:13.601
All right.

32:41.328 --> 32:43.163
Thanks for meeting me.

32:43.197 --> 32:45.466
I don't usually meet clients
outside the courthouse.

32:45.499 --> 32:48.435
Professional, though some
judges might disagree.

32:51.004 --> 32:56.109
- You okay?
- The plan.

32:56.143 --> 33:00.648
When I got back, Craig said
something that has me freaked.

33:03.116 --> 33:04.853
Like?

33:04.886 --> 33:09.156
I think something happened
to the mule's girlfriend.

33:11.793 --> 33:14.929
Okay, you have to tell
Winston.

33:14.963 --> 33:15.763
Yeah, right.

33:15.797 --> 33:16.865
I'm being serious.

33:16.898 --> 33:19.132
It's the only way to protect
yourself.

33:19.166 --> 33:22.135
Assault, impersonating a
police officer, grand larceny.

33:22.169 --> 33:24.973
Craig Bayonne's illustrious
body of work goes on and on.

33:28.408 --> 33:30.812
- No charges of murder?
- Not yet.

33:34.716 --> 33:35.884
Anything else?

33:41.523 --> 33:44.391
In the tow pound, on the
wall in the waiting room,

33:44.424 --> 33:46.728
there's this picture of a
mountain,

33:46.761 --> 33:48.462
like Everest or something.

33:48.495 --> 33:50.364
Years ago, it must have been
put up to take the edge off.

33:50.397 --> 33:52.399
Like a plant you didn't have to
water.

33:53.902 --> 33:57.337
I asked the lady at window
five who has been there forever

33:57.371 --> 34:00.542
if she knew where it was
or who put it up or why?

34:01.543 --> 34:04.512
Not a clue, not a clue.

34:04.546 --> 34:06.046
She never even thought to ask.

34:08.550 --> 34:11.853
That's why I knew I had to
get the fuck out of there.

34:11.886 --> 34:16.089
And when I did, I'd find that
mountain.

34:16.123 --> 34:18.693
You know, most thieves pick a
beach,

34:18.726 --> 34:21.495
you know, nice views,
kayaking, all that stuff.

34:21.529 --> 34:26.233
- I'm not most thieves.
- Right.

34:27.869 --> 34:29.069
And I don't wanna live my life
looking

34:29.101 --> 34:30.370
at lost opportunities.

34:35.877 --> 34:36.710
I'm with you.

34:40.246 --> 34:41.081
It's crazy to think

34:42.382 --> 34:44.284
someone's gonna see 15 million
dollars,

34:45.319 --> 34:48.487
all in one room, all at once.

34:51.224 --> 34:53.061
Think of the lives that could
change.

34:59.399 --> 35:01.569
- Be right back.
- All right.

35:48.850 --> 35:50.317
Need a refill, hun?

35:50.350 --> 35:51.351
Thank you.

35:55.957 --> 35:58.960
- Little more?
- I got it.

36:03.998 --> 36:06.668
Should you get back to grinding
the gears of bureaucracy?

36:06.701 --> 36:08.268
Mm-hmm.

36:10.170 --> 36:11.806
- All you had to do-
- I know.

36:11.839 --> 36:12.640
I told you.

36:12.674 --> 36:14.408
Did I not tell you, Casi?

36:16.476 --> 36:18.345
You couldn't just shut up and do
your job?

36:18.378 --> 36:19.814
Selling mattresses is a job.

36:19.847 --> 36:21.214
Mmm, Lord.

36:21.248 --> 36:23.551
My guys, I gotta look out for
them.

36:23.584 --> 36:26.654
By making me do this
thing I don't wanna do?

36:26.688 --> 36:28.455
It's not about letting me down.

36:28.488 --> 36:31.626
Your clients, what about them?

36:31.659 --> 36:33.226
This is a bullshit
complaint and you know it.

36:33.260 --> 36:35.228
Then apologize to the
judge.

36:35.262 --> 36:36.130
To Cymbeline?

36:36.164 --> 36:37.197
Fuck that.

36:37.230 --> 36:38.900
I'd rather eat her fucking ankle
weights.

36:40.702 --> 36:41.936
Six months suspension.

36:44.204 --> 36:47.742
I don't think they'll disbar,
maybe.

36:55.449 --> 36:56.283
Casi.

37:05.392 --> 37:06.460
What are you gonna do?

37:08.062 --> 37:09.262
I hear Cuba's nice.

37:10.363 --> 37:11.264
And now you're just being an
asshole.

37:11.298 --> 37:12.499
What do you want me to say?

37:12.533 --> 37:13.735
This is what I do.

37:13.768 --> 37:15.570
Excuse me, for busting my ass,

37:15.603 --> 37:16.938
trying to level the playing
field.

37:16.971 --> 37:19.707
You can't fight everyone,
every step of the way.

37:20.742 --> 37:23.177
We're all on the same side.

37:23.211 --> 37:24.545
Maybe that's the problem.

37:34.387 --> 37:35.223
You were right.

37:36.090 --> 37:36.991
Of course I was.

37:38.458 --> 37:40.260
About what?

37:40.293 --> 37:41.929
The strong will always eat the
weak.

37:41.963 --> 37:44.132
No, however could that be.

37:47.135 --> 37:48.435
Tough week for you, champ?

37:49.670 --> 37:51.639
All right, come on,

37:51.672 --> 37:55.243
a night of heroic drinking
and revenge fantasies, on me.

38:00.347 --> 38:02.517
Who wants this job anyway?

38:06.087 --> 38:08.990
Bright side? At least now you
can see if wonder ears likes

38:09.023 --> 38:10.323
you for more than your docket.

38:12.093 --> 38:15.263
Lea Deleon used me, she lied.

38:15.295 --> 38:17.565
Stop the presses.

38:17.598 --> 38:19.100
- Bigfoots a fiction?
- Oh no, no,

38:19.133 --> 38:20.101
deal's going down all right.

38:20.134 --> 38:22.603
Just not the date she told vice.

38:29.777 --> 38:30.611
Huh.

38:32.345 --> 38:33.748
This is crazy.

38:33.781 --> 38:35.415
I don't know if you're
serious or just smoking crack.

38:35.448 --> 38:38.019
- I'm 100% both.
- Then obviously, no

38:38.052 --> 38:39.654
Don't be fucking so
close-minded.

38:39.687 --> 38:42.322
No, no, let me save you time.

38:42.355 --> 38:43.825
I will, under no circumstance,

38:43.858 --> 38:46.194
participate in an attempt
to steal millions of dollars

38:46.227 --> 38:50.164
